column2: "Hee hee! Nice work! I don't even have to read your report to see that. You really had some fine moves!"
"You sure made those hostiles dance and suffer before you wiped them out completely. You're an amazing Ranger."
"It's way more fun to kill, kill, and kill some more with you than it is with others."
"I hope we can do this again soon."
"And maybe next time we can make even more hostiles suffer and then suffer some more!"
